These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  coach, chef, mechanic, doctor, software-developer
5 different games are played: backgammon, chess, mah-jongg, poker, billiard
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the doctor##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the coach##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the chef is on the far left##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
6. the coach is in the middle##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Job   | chef | mechanic | coach | software-developer | doctor |
| Game   | billiard    | backgammon | mah-jongg     | poker       | chess  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
City: london, venice, hannover, hamburg, berlin
House: wooden, art-deco, tower, ranch-style, farmhouse
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
5. the person traveling to venice is the tower house##1
6. the farmhouse house is the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| City      | venice | hannover | london | hamburg | berlin |
| House   | tower  | ranch-style   | wooden       | art-deco    | farmhouse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
City: hannover, new-york, marseilles, london, paris
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory, lavender, purple, blue
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| City        | marseilles | london | new-york | hannover | paris |
| Color   | ivory  | yellow      | blue | lavender | purple      |

