.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, pakistani, colombian, mexican, german
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, purple, yellow, red, ivory
1. the german is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese        | colombian | pakistani | german |
| Color     | amber | red | ivory  | purple   | yellow |

