.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, taxi, roller, boat
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, woodworking, baking, drawing, camping
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Transport    | taxi   | jet-ski     | trike   | roller         | boat |
| Hobby   | reading | drawing | baking | camping | woodworking     |

