.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, iced-tea, fanta, milk
5 different games are played: chess, backgammon, canasta, monopoly, mah-jongg
1. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing canasta is the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Beverage       | fanta   | iced-tea   | tea | milk | juice |
| Game   | backgammon | canasta | monopoly   | mah-jongg | chess       |

