.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, september, december, june, august
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, helicopter, jet-ski, roller
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Birthday     | september   | december  | august      | july | june     |
| Transport   | jet-ski | helicopter | quad-bike | subway   | roller |

