.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, pear, carrot, cranberry, eggplant
5 different games are played: poker, go, bridge, domino, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating pear##1
7. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Food     | pear | cauliflower       | eggplant | cranberry | carrot    |
| Game   | domino   | mah-jongg | bridge  | go     | poker |

