.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, rugby, volleyball, baseball, soccer
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, begonia, zinnia, lily, tulip
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsbegonia##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Sport         | baseball | skiing | volleyball | soccer | rugby |
| Flower   | zinnia       | lily   | tulip         | begonia   | poppy   |

