.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, april, august, may, december
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, prince, old-henry, bolivar
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Birthday   | december | may | april | august | july |
| Cigar           | bolivar      | aristoff    | old-henry  | montecristo     | prince     |

