4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing poker##1
7. the person playing billiard is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
