.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, coral, apricot, aquamarine, yellow
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, rose, tulip, bellflower, daffodil
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Color    | lavender | aquamarine          | apricot    | yellow | coral  |
| Flower   | tulip  | daffodil | zinnia | bellflower | rose |

