.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, rose, dahlia, lily
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, dannemann, tiparillo, alhambra
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who growslily is the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person who growsdahlia is in the middle##1
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Flower   | rose | bellflower      | dahlia | daisy | lily |
| Cigar     | tiparillo  | pall-mall | old-henry     | alhambra     | dannemann  |

