.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, ship, bike, van, subway
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, spy, family, drama, musical
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport      | subway | bike | scooter      | van | ship      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | drama       | scientific | musical  | family |

