.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, water, tea, milk, fanta
There 5 different types of food: pear, corn, lime, zucchini, blueberry
1. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Beverage   | water   | milk  | juice | fanta | tea  |
| Food         | pear | lime | zucchini  | blueberry    | corn |

