.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, domino, whist, backgammon
House: cottage, tower, art-deco, wooden, gothic-revival
1. the tower house is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
3. the wooden house is on the far left##1
4. the art-deco house is the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Game   | backgammon     | domino       | snooker     | scrabble  | whist  |
| House      | wooden | cottage | tower | gothic-revival | art-deco |

