.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different games are played: scrabble, go, billiard, poker, backgammon
There 5 different types of food: radish, cabbage, mango, broccoli, cauliflower
1. the person eating cabbage is in the middle##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating radish##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person eating mango is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Game   | go | backgammon | billiard | scrabble | poker |
| Food           | cauliflower | broccoli  | cabbage    | radish  | mango   |

 